# Ignore all markdown files except the official README.md and SETUP.md
*.md
!README.md
!SETUP.md
!setup.md

# Ignore the entire Docs directory containing plans and audits, except SETUP.md
Docs/**
!Docs/SETUP.md
!Docs/setup.md

